{
  "stem": "25114.7",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were with the partisan right to the liberation, too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we stayed there, trying to make a living.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My husband was sort of-- we didn't have any money-- not much.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We bought something, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the time that we-- he worked in the factory there, and then he used to go to the-- to the villages and repair people's saddles-- you know, peasants-- everything.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had very little money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We brought some food with us, too-- a lot of food from things.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The territories in Poland began to be liberated, one by one.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And certain parts of Poland, which were liberated later-- Krakow, in-- in Silesia, you know-- and Katowice.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And these places weren't ruined by war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were intact, and they were-- they had lots of household goods and clothes and everything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But they don't have any food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we had food, and we didn't have any other household goods or clothes or any other consumer goods.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my husband took a friend who was with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were living in the same-- we bought two adjoining rooms in Chelm when we lived there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he took him, and they took suitcases, and they filled the suitcases with food, and they went to those places that were freshly liberated and-- and got some-- exchanged the food for the other goods and brought the goods and sold them to the people who didn't have [LAUGHS] any food.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's what you did in Russia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because one place has everything, one place had nothing of thing-- one had something else, and the other one-- that's how the speculate-- the black market existed in the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because it was very-- not centralized.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everything was sort of-- Nobody knew where-- what-- what was where.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
